casebody.data:
Robert J. TRIFFIN, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
JETRO HOLDINGS, LLC, (d/b/a) Jetro, and Tykeeya B. Mitchell, Defendants,
and
JP Morgan Chase Bank, N.A., Garnishee-Respondent. C-985 September Term 2016
079105 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004371-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
